data.description: Welcome to your future home nestled in the heart of Warner Robins! Situated in one of Houston County's most established neighborhoods, this residence offers a prime location near the Houston Medical Center and Robins Air Force Base, ensuring convenience and accessibility for your daily needs.  Embrace the outdoors with Briarcliff Park just a short stroll across the street, inviting you to enjoy nature and recreational activities right at your doorstep. This charming abode boasts 3 bedrooms and 1.5 bathrooms, providing a comfortable and welcoming atmosphere for you and your family.  Discover the timeless elegance of hardwood floors throughout the majority of the home, adding warmth and character to each room. The thoughtful design includes a secondary living area, offering flexibility and space for various lifestyle needs.  The detached 1-car garage at the rear of the driveway is not just a parking space; it doubles as a versatile workshop, ideal for storage or pursuing your favorite hobbies. Unleash the potential within this space to create your own haven or workspace.  Opportunity awaits in this residence with numerous possibilities to make it uniquely yours. Don't miss out - call today to schedule a showing and unlock the door to your new home in Warner Robins!
